'''百慕達眾議院'''（{{lang-en|House of Assembly of Bermuda}}），是[[英國海外領土|英國海外領土]][[百慕達|百慕達]][[百慕大议会|議會]]的[[下議院|下議院]]，共有36名議員，5年一任，以單議席[[選區|選區]]制選出。

==歷史==
眾議院原本是百慕大議會唯一議院，1620年首次舉行會議。當時會議地點設於殖民地首府[[圣乔治斯|圣乔治斯]]{{le|聖彼得教堂 (聖喬治斯)|St. Peter's Church, St. George's|聖彼得教堂}}直到{{le|議會大樓 (百慕達)|State House, Bermuda|議會大樓}}於同年落成為止。1815年，會議地點隨著首府遷至[[哈密尔顿_(百慕大)|哈密尔顿]]而移師到舊市政廳舉行。1826年後，眾議院會議在會議大廈舉行<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.parliament.bm/History_of_Parliament_Buildings.aspx|title=Bermuda Parliament|work=parliament.bm|accessdate=15 September 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306000334/http://parliament.bm/history_of_parliament_buildings.aspx|archive-date=2016-03-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gov.bm/portal/server.pt?open=512&objID=897&&PageID=232433&mode=2&in_hi_userid=2&cached=true |title=Website of the Government of Bermuda: House of Assembly |accessdate=2016-03-15 |archive-date=2012-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121118082155/http://www.gov.bm/portal/server.pt?open=512&objID=897&&PageID=232433&mode=2&in_hi_userid=2&cached=true |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.fco.gov.uk/resources/en/pdf/publications/overseas-territories-white-paper-0612/ot-wp-0612-chapter4 |title=Government of the United Kingdom White Paper on British Overseas Territories 2012: Making Government work better |accessdate=2016-03-15 |archive-date=2012-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121019015331/http://www.fco.gov.uk/resources/en/pdf/publications/overseas-territories-white-paper-0612/ot-wp-0612-chapter4 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.parliament.bm/Facts_about_Bermuda_.aspx|title=Bermuda Parliament|work=parliament.bm|accessdate=15 September 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305102927/http://parliament.bm/facts_about_bermuda_.aspx|archive-date=2016-03-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

